'Cex' is a musical project run by Rjyan Claybrook Kidwell and started in 1998 at
the age of 16. Although Cex and Kidwell are frequently used interchangeably, Cex
occasionally expands to several people at sporadic points, such as particular
tours or albums. In the past it has included Kidwell's musical associates,
friends, touring partners, or high school bandmates.<ref>|title=Biography:
Cex|last=Potts|first=Diana |publisher=Allmusic|accessdate=26 April 2010}}</ref>
